data.description:
This property in West Palm Beach offers a fantastic opportunity for both comfortable living and potential income generation. Situated near I-95 and the airport, this location provides convenient access to major transportation routes and amenities.The residence features three bedrooms and two bathrooms, providing ample space for a family or individuals seeking room to spread out. The interior boasts a well-designed layout, with a bright and airy atmosphere throughout. The living areas are perfect for entertaining.The bedrooms are well-appointed and offer a peaceful retreat. The property also includes a separate income-producing studio, which can be utilized as a rental unit or as a private space for guests or extended family members. One of the standout features of this property is the roof, which was replaced in 2015. This ensures peace of mind for the new owner, as they can enjoy the benefits of a newer roof without the worry of immediate maintenance or replacement costs.

Outside, the property offers a spacious yard, perfect for outdoor activities or potential landscaping projects. The location near I-95 and the airport provides easy access to nearby attractions, shopping centers, restaurants, and entertainment options.

Overall, this property in West Palm Beach presents an excellent opportunity for those seeking a comfortable home with the added benefit of a separate income-producing studio. With its convenient location, updated roof, and spacious layout, this property is sure to appeal to a wide range of buyers.
